article.description: — Kellen Amos had 20 points in Central Connecticut's 82-73 victory over Hartford on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Amos' 20 lead Central Connecticut over Hartford 82-73
article.linkText: Amos' 20 lead Central Connecticut over Hartford 82-73
article.story:
WEST HARTFORD, Conn. -- — Kellen Amos had 20 points in Central Connecticut's 82-73 victory over Hartford on Wednesday night.

Amos added three steals for the Blue Devils (7-19). Andre Snoddy scored 18 points and added five rebounds. Davonte Sweatman recorded 12 points.

Michael Dunne led the Hawks (5-20), finishing with 24 points and six rebounds. Kurtis Henderson added 17 points and five assists for Hartford.
